        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer196231745" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9689924532101018833">Lewis is an American student going to school in Oxford. When his roomate discovers a newspaper article about a legendary beast (an aurochs) that was sighted, they both go on a weekend adventure to try and see it. What they discover however, is a cairn that transports them into another world-the world of Albion.<br/><br/>This book was seriously amazing. I picked it up in the store because the cover caught my eye, but I didn&apos;t expect to get swept up in it like I did. It is an amazing fantasy story, with wri</span>
  <span id="freeText9689924532101018833" style="display:none">Lewis is an American student going to school in Oxford. When his roomate discovers a newspaper article about a legendary beast (an aurochs) that was sighted, they both go on a weekend adventure to try and see it. What they discover however, is a cairn that transports them into another world-the world of Albion.<br /><br />This book was seriously amazing. I picked it up in the store because the cover caught my eye, but I didn't expect to get swept up in it like I did. It is an amazing fantasy story, with writing so beautiful and descriptive I felt almost as if I were in Albion too! I really enjoyed this story and would recommend it to anyone!<br /><br />Albion Forever! :)</span>
