<span id="freeTextContainer12030677405816863535">Tricky for me to rate this book. I read through sections quickly, but felt that not much was happening. Then I would put the book aside, take a break from it, and then try again. Since this is the first of a series I suspect that much of the action is coming in the next book. I&apos;m just not sure I will continue. I really like it when I get caught up in a story and I feel as if I am in the story. When I feel connected to the characters, and can&apos;t wait to see what happens. I just didn&apos;t feel that wa</span>
